1
00:00:01,320 --> 00:00:03,740
My name is Oliver Queen.

2
00:00:04,140 --> 00:00:06,650
After five years on a hellish island,

3
00:00:07,350 --> 00:00:09,660
I have come home with only one goal...

4
00:00:10,230 --> 00:00:12,450
to save my city.

5
00:00:12,730 --> 00:00:16,130
But to do so,I can't be the killer I once was.

6
00:00:17,850 --> 00:00:21,990
To honor my friend's memory,I must be someone else.

7
00:00:22,680 --> 00:00:26,450
I must be something else.

8
00:00:27,160 --> 00:00:28,750
Previously on "Arrow"...

9
00:00:28,870 --> 00:00:30,240
This one's no longer of use to us.

10
00:00:30,370 --> 00:00:31,750
Wait.He could still be useful.

11
00:00:31,860 --> 00:00:32,770
She's right.

12
00:00:32,900 --> 00:00:36,200
Once we get rid of his friends,we'll need him to lead us to the grave.

13
00:00:36,320 --> 00:00:37,900
You're going back to the island.

14
00:00:38,650 --> 00:00:40,000
Look,you already lost your dad.

15
00:00:40,110 --> 00:00:41,210
Your mom,she's still here.

16
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:42,660
And I'm sure she'd love to see you.

17
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:44,570
I'm not going to that prison.

18
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:46,780
It's the only way I know how to hurt her.

19
00:00:46,970 --> 00:00:48,310
And I want to hate you.

20
00:00:49,460 --> 00:00:50,930
But I can't.

21
00:00:53,140 --> 00:00:55,440
I didn't think that there were secrets kept between us.

22
00:00:55,550 --> 00:00:58,120
Mom...what are you hiding?

23
00:01:00,900 --> 00:01:03,420
My name is Moira Dearden Queen.

24
00:01:03,580 --> 00:01:06,630
I am the acting CEO of Queen Consolidated.

25
00:01:07,190 --> 00:01:09,600
And,God forgive me,I have failed this city.

26
00:01:11,210 --> 00:01:15,890
I have been complicit in an undertaking with one horrible purpose...

27
00:01:20,210 --> 00:01:23,010
to destroy the Glades and everyone in it.

28
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:27,530
If you reside in the Glades,please,you need to get out now.

29
00:01:27,780 --> 00:01:31,040
Your lives and the lives of your children depend on it.

30
00:01:32,010 --> 00:01:33,270
Please.

31
00:01:33,730 --> 00:01:35,560
Warden says we got to evacuate.

32
00:01:37,850 --> 00:01:39,100
Help me get these out of here.

33
00:01:39,210 --> 00:01:40,510
What about the inmates?

34
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,920
Leave 'em.

35
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:28,490
Over here,let me out.

36
00:02:31,070 --> 00:02:32,810
No.Give me the keys!

37
00:02:32,970 --> 00:02:38,110
No,no,too violent.Too Sloppy,too stupid.

38
00:02:38,820 --> 00:02:40,980
Too...ambitious.

39
00:02:41,650 --> 00:02:43,010
You.

40
00:02:43,470 --> 00:02:45,130
I love your work.

41
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:46,990
Big future.

42
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:49,280
Hey,be careful.

43
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,400
There's liable to be aftershocks.

44
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,210
Oh,I'm counting on it.

